<item>
            <title>[CXF-4776] UsernameTokenValidator do not validate that password is not provided.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-4776</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is an issue for both WS-Policy and WSS4JInInterceptor configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If I include an incorrect Password I get the expected authentication error.  If I actually remove the password I get no authentication failure.  The UsernameTokenValidator only checks that the username is provided.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
